1
00:00:32,260 --> 00:00:33,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ashiya?</font>

2
00:00:33,000 --> 00:00:35,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, sorry. Did I wake you up?</font>

3
00:00:35,900 --> 00:00:37,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't sleep?</font>

4
00:00:37,250 --> 00:00:40,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I just had this kind of scary dream.</font>

5
00:00:42,300 --> 00:00:44,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then want to sleep with me?</font>

6
00:00:45,250 --> 00:00:50,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? U-Uh, Sano...</font>

7
00:00:50,010 --> 00:00:51,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um?!</font>

8
00:00:51,440 --> 00:00:52,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just get in already.</font>

9
00:00:52,970 --> 00:00:54,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My bed's getting cold.</font>

10
00:00:55,500 --> 00:00:58,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why the hell are your feet so cold?</font>

11
00:00:58,100 --> 00:00:59,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>His feet...</i></font>

12
00:00:59,340 --> 00:01:01,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>His feet are so toasty!</i></font>

13
00:01:02,690 --> 00:01:05,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Er, S-Sano...</font>

14
00:01:07,280 --> 00:01:08,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think I'm just gonna sleep alone—</font>

15
00:01:08,860 --> 00:01:10,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop yapping.</font>

16
00:01:10,480 --> 00:01:11,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's not a lot of room.</font>

17
00:01:11,760 --> 00:01:13,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is that the problem here?!</i></font>

18
00:01:13,910 --> 00:01:16,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you sleep like this...</font>

19
00:01:17,240 --> 00:01:19,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure you won't have 
any more... scary dreams...</font>

20
00:01:20,370 --> 00:01:23,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wait, he was still half asleep?!</i></font>

21
00:01:27,990 --> 00:01:29,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I might not have any scary dreams,</i></font>

22
00:01:29,810 --> 00:01:31,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but I can't sleep like this!</i></font>

23
00:01:33,850 --> 00:01:34,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Whatever!</i></font>

24
00:01:35,620 --> 00:01:37,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Gotta take what I can get!</i></font>

25
00:01:40,630 --> 00:01:44,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can hear his heartbeat...</i></font>

26
00:01:47,760 --> 00:01:49,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's so reassuring.</i></font>

27
00:01:52,080 --> 00:01:54,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good morning!</font>

28
00:01:55,020 --> 00:01:56,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a new day!</font>

29
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:59,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right! We have the 
early shift this morning!</font>

30
00:02:00,750 --> 00:02:02,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-Wh-Wha?!</font>

31
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:06,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why the hell are you two sharing a bed?!</font>

32
00:02:07,020 --> 00:02:12,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had a scary dream, 
so I ended up sleeping with Sano.</font>

33
00:02:12,630 --> 00:02:14,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll get ready real quick.</font>

34
00:02:14,670 --> 00:02:18,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh, he wandered into my bed 
again while sleep-drunk, huh?</i></font>

35
00:02:18,850 --> 00:02:22,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O-Okay, I'm just gonna wait outside.</font>

36
00:02:22,390 --> 00:02:23,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, sorry!</font>

37
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:30,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A guy in his second year of high school 
sleeping with another guy</i></font>

38
00:02:30,320 --> 00:02:33,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>because he had a bad dream 
is not normal, right?</i></font>

39
00:02:33,530 --> 00:02:37,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yikes, Nakatsu. Your aura 
is the color of jealousy.</font>

40
00:04:16,250 --> 00:04:20,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font size="30"><font face="Impact"><font color="#ebe166">I Was the Same</font></font></font></font>

41
00:04:19,540 --> 00:04:22,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, look at all the people!</font>

42
00:04:22,860 --> 00:04:26,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Outside visitors are allowed in today.</font>

43
00:04:27,110 --> 00:04:30,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, Kayashima, you're doing 
something independent too?</font>

44
00:04:27,890 --> 00:04:29,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="14"><font color="#44443f"><b>This individual is authorized
 to vend independently.</b></font></font></font></font>

45
00:04:27,890 --> 00:04:29,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="18"><font color="#44443f"><b>Kayashima Daiki</b></font></font></font></font>

46
00:04:30,530 --> 00:04:31,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

47
00:04:31,340 --> 00:04:32,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's that?</font>

48
00:04:32,510 --> 00:04:33,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This?</font>

49
00:04:33,680 --> 00:04:35,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you do with that thing?</font>

50
00:04:36,550 --> 00:04:37,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You want to know?</font>

51
00:04:38,410 --> 00:04:40,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here, a spirit photo.</font>

52
00:04:55,090 --> 00:05:00,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial Black"><font size="18">{\an9}<font color="#4d3d75">I'll photograph your ancestors
<font color="#d3cd9a"><font face="Comic Sans MS">(or guardian spirit) <font face="Impact"><font color="#a4363c">Low price</font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font>

53
00:04:55,090 --> 00:04:58,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, it's a business
profiting off my hobby.</font>

54
00:05:02,640 --> 00:05:06,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sekime and the others were all excited 
about girls from other schools,</font>

55
00:05:06,760 --> 00:05:08,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but there sure are a lot of them.</font>

56
00:05:08,750 --> 00:05:10,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So cute!</font>

57
00:05:10,960 --> 00:05:12,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He looks like a real girl!</font>

58
00:05:14,280 --> 00:05:15,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

59
00:05:15,400 --> 00:05:20,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>All eyes are on the dorm showdown, 
but the rankings remain unchanged!</i></font>

60
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:25,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="16"><font color="#8b7d91">Dorm 1\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hDorm 2\h\h\h\h\h\h\hDorm 3</font></font></font></font>

61
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:21,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Still, it's neck and neck!</i></font>

62
00:05:21,440 --> 00:05:22,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There's no room for mistakes.</i></font>

63
00:05:22,950 --> 00:05:26,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Which team will be the one 
to take the win?</i></font>

64
00:05:26,710 --> 00:05:29,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh, this is Nanba-senpai's class.</i></font>

65
00:05:27,670 --> 00:05:29,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="30">{\an1}<font color="#6af8dd"><b>Mystery Show</b></font></font></font></font>

66
00:05:27,670 --> 00:05:29,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="30"><font color="#827e7d"><b>Who really did it?!</b></font></font></font></font>

67
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:30,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Senpai!</font>

68
00:05:30,960 --> 00:05:31,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is for you.</font>

69
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:34,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, thanks.</font>

70
00:05:34,420 --> 00:05:36,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't believe the line!</font>

71
00:05:36,450 --> 00:05:38,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, we've been lucky.</font>

72
00:05:38,860 --> 00:05:40,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This was no suicide.</font>

73
00:05:41,540 --> 00:05:43,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a murderer's trick.</font>

74
00:05:43,340 --> 00:05:44,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who are you?</font>

75
00:05:44,960 --> 00:05:46,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am Akechi Kojiro,</font>

76
00:05:46,540 --> 00:05:50,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the great-grandson of the 
renowned detective Akechi Goro.</font>

77
00:05:52,440 --> 00:05:55,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">B-But what evidence do you have
to say this was a murder?</font>

78
00:05:55,540 --> 00:05:59,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You there, lovely lady. 
May I ask for your assistance?</font>

79
00:05:59,930 --> 00:06:01,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Me?</font>

80
00:06:02,290 --> 00:06:06,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The victim was practicing a dance 
with a partner in this very spot.</font>

81
00:06:06,650 --> 00:06:07,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just like this.</font>

82
00:06:09,090 --> 00:06:14,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would a dancer drink poisoned wine while 
practicing for tomorrow's competition?</font>

83
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:15,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just like this?</font>

84
00:06:18,220 --> 00:06:19,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Nakao-kun?!</i></font>

85
00:06:20,970 --> 00:06:22,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, what are you doing?</font>

86
00:06:22,800 --> 00:06:24,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was wondering where you were!</font>

87
00:06:24,640 --> 00:06:27,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I didn't get to see him 
at all yesterday.</font>

88
00:06:27,730 --> 00:06:29,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry!</font>

89
00:06:29,760 --> 00:06:31,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, wait.</font>

90
00:06:31,770 --> 00:06:34,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please let me take a picture 
with you! Just one!</font>

91
00:06:34,980 --> 00:06:35,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please!</font>

92
00:06:35,990 --> 00:06:38,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, sure, just one.</font>

93
00:06:40,840 --> 00:06:43,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">While you were gone, 
we used him to bring in customers,</font>

94
00:06:43,270 --> 00:06:45,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but the girls are just fawning over him.</font>

95
00:06:45,230 --> 00:06:46,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Must be nice.</font>

96
00:06:46,620 --> 00:06:49,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, now a twofie!</font>

97
00:06:49,050 --> 00:06:49,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

98
00:06:49,620 --> 00:06:50,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey...</font>

99
00:06:51,510 --> 00:06:53,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Hurry up and take it!</font>

100
00:06:52,090 --> 00:06:52,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ashiya?</font>

101
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:55,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing?</font>

102
00:06:55,260 --> 00:06:58,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're short-staffed, 
so get back to work already!</font>

103
00:07:00,720 --> 00:07:02,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks, Ashiya.</font>

104
00:07:02,460 --> 00:07:04,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're a lifesaver.</font>

105
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:05,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't know how to get away from them.</font>

106
00:07:06,730 --> 00:07:08,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ashiya? What's wrong?</font>

107
00:07:09,510 --> 00:07:10,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing.</font>

108
00:07:12,460 --> 00:07:14,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's his problem?</font>

109
00:07:14,830 --> 00:07:17,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, it's Alice! How cute!</font>

110
00:07:17,490 --> 00:07:19,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'd never know you're a guy!</font>

111
00:07:19,220 --> 00:07:20,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, hey! What grade are you in?</font>

112
00:07:20,850 --> 00:07:22,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I take your picture? Can I?</font>

113
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:29,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are girls so crazy 
about guys in girls' clothes?</font>

114
00:07:29,630 --> 00:07:34,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To be more precise, 
<i>hot</i> guys in girls' clothing.</font>

115
00:07:35,420 --> 00:07:38,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Be on your guard, you sweet thing.</font>

116
00:07:40,880 --> 00:07:44,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The night always has you in its sights.</font>

117
00:07:44,540 --> 00:07:46,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That voice...</i></font>

118
00:07:48,540 --> 00:07:51,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yikes, Himejima Masao!</i></font>

119
00:07:51,220 --> 00:07:54,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What comforts this dweller of the night...</font>

120
00:07:55,330 --> 00:07:57,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is your sweet blood.</font>

121
00:08:01,840 --> 00:08:06,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I invite you to 3-B's haunted house, 
produced by Oscar M. Himejima.</font>

122
00:08:06,300 --> 00:08:07,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do come along.</font>

123
00:08:07,280 --> 00:08:10,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="18">{\an8}<font color="#923e6b">Haunted House</font></font></font></font>

124
00:08:07,280 --> 00:08:11,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, so sorry for poaching 
all of your customers!</font>

125
00:08:11,920 --> 00:08:13,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Farewell!</font>

126
00:08:14,790 --> 00:08:17,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What was that about?</font>

127
00:08:17,080 --> 00:08:19,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn you, Masao!</font>

128
00:08:19,280 --> 00:08:20,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not only did you poach our customers,</font>

129
00:08:20,870 --> 00:08:23,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but you also put your grubby 
mitts all over Mizuki!</font>

130
00:08:23,720 --> 00:08:25,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Paging all beauty pageant contestants.</i></font>

131
00:08:25,650 --> 00:08:27,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Please gather at the special stage.</i></font>

132
00:08:28,610 --> 00:08:30,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on. That's our cue, Ashiya!</font>

133
00:08:30,940 --> 00:08:33,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gosh, it's one thing after another!</font>

134
00:08:34,700 --> 00:08:38,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn you, Masao. I'm gonna beat yer ass.</font>

135
00:08:38,670 --> 00:08:41,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I deliberately missed 
with the flower pot I dropped.</font>

136
00:08:41,450 --> 00:08:42,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good.</font>

137
00:08:43,580 --> 00:08:46,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's that first-year on the karate team.</i></font>

138
00:08:46,700 --> 00:08:47,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And?</font>

139
00:08:47,640 --> 00:08:49,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How did Ashiya Mizuki look after that?</font>

140
00:08:49,550 --> 00:08:51,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think the threat was received.</font>

141
00:08:51,950 --> 00:08:53,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The hell?!</i></font>

142
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:54,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen here.</font>

143
00:08:54,860 --> 00:08:59,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This year, Dorm 1 has to win the 
grand prize no matter what.</font>

144
00:09:00,830 --> 00:09:01,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

145
00:09:01,530 --> 00:09:02,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

146
00:09:03,540 --> 00:09:06,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Er, it's nothing.</font>

147
00:09:06,350 --> 00:09:09,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hang on, that means the incident
during the chicken fight was also...</i></font>

148
00:09:09,360 --> 00:09:11,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've got nice legs.</font>

149
00:09:13,780 --> 00:09:14,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go!</font>

150
00:09:15,110 --> 00:09:16,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was just a compliment.</font>

151
00:09:16,900 --> 00:09:18,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't jump out of your skin.</font>

152
00:09:18,710 --> 00:09:20,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll do what I want!</font>

153
00:09:20,150 --> 00:09:22,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you think you're
 doing, you idiot?!</font>

154
00:09:22,740 --> 00:09:23,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kujo.</font>

155
00:09:24,870 --> 00:09:27,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard everything.</font>

156
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:30,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">From your little friends in Dorm 1!</font>

157
00:09:30,780 --> 00:09:32,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, huh?</font>

158
00:09:32,070 --> 00:09:33,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's nobody here.</font>

159
00:09:34,150 --> 00:09:35,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Either way,</font>

160
00:09:35,450 --> 00:09:38,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't care how dirty you guys play,</font>

161
00:09:38,020 --> 00:09:40,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not lettin' you lay
 a finger on Mizuki!</font>

162
00:09:40,630 --> 00:09:42,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And don't you forget it!</font>

163
00:09:47,230 --> 00:09:49,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nakatsu, where the heck have you been?</font>

164
00:09:49,630 --> 00:09:51,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's showtime in five minutes!</font>

165
00:09:52,250 --> 00:09:53,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Izumi!</font>

166
00:09:53,080 --> 00:09:53,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

167
00:09:54,300 --> 00:09:55,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mizuki's in danger.</font>

168
00:09:57,720 --> 00:10:00,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ladies and gentlemen!</i></font>

169
00:10:00,380 --> 00:10:03,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's what you've all been waiting for, 
today's special event:</i></font>

170
00:10:03,160 --> 00:10:07,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Osaka Academy's famous beauty pageant!</i></font>

171
00:10:07,460 --> 00:10:12,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We of the broadcasting club and the
executive committee will be your hosts.</font>

172
00:10:12,260 --> 00:10:14,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Now, over to our on-stage commentary!</i></font>

173
00:10:14,670 --> 00:10:16,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, comment.</font>

174
00:10:16,730 --> 00:10:23,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Only the twelve you see here made it past
the rigorous elimination round, comment.</font>

175
00:10:24,380 --> 00:10:26,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want to go home!</i></font>

176
00:10:26,170 --> 00:10:31,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now let's introduce the top four who 
currently have the most votes, comment!</font>

177
00:10:31,930 --> 00:10:34,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll begin with contestant number 15.</font>

178
00:10:34,850 --> 00:10:37,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A favorite among the first-years,</font>

179
00:10:37,310 --> 00:10:40,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it's the fresh-faced Kadoma Shotaro!</font>

180
00:10:40,190 --> 00:10:43,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Moving on, we've got contestant number 18.</font>

181
00:10:43,180 --> 00:10:45,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You already know him
 as last year's winner.</font>

182
00:10:45,460 --> 00:10:47,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's Nakao Senri!</font>

183
00:10:47,440 --> 00:10:49,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Next is contestant 23,</font>

184
00:10:49,710 --> 00:10:52,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the talk of the town 
who's back from living abroad!</font>

185
00:10:52,200 --> 00:10:53,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ever since he transferred here,</font>

186
00:10:53,900 --> 00:10:56,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">he's seen a stellar rise in popularity!</font>

187
00:10:56,200 --> 00:10:58,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's Ashiya Mizuki!</font>

188
00:10:58,460 --> 00:11:04,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then we've got contestant 34, who made 
the cut despite being a last-minute entry!</font>

189
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:07,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the shy "I'd Like to Stay Anonymous"!</font>

190
00:11:07,460 --> 00:11:10,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And now, on to the talent program!</font>

191
00:11:10,140 --> 00:11:13,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Contestant number 5 will be singing opera.</font>

192
00:11:14,970 --> 00:11:17,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I knew it was the Dorm 1 guys.</font>

193
00:11:17,180 --> 00:11:17,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go.</font>

194
00:11:17,940 --> 00:11:18,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go where?</font>

195
00:11:18,800 --> 00:11:20,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The pageant's already
in full swing, right?</font>

196
00:11:20,740 --> 00:11:22,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If they're going to make a move,
it'll be now.</font>

197
00:11:23,660 --> 00:11:29,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We'd like to thank all of our finalists
for their unique performances, comment!</i></font>

198
00:11:29,120 --> 00:11:31,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Now let's get to voting, comment!</i></font>

199
00:11:33,500 --> 00:11:35,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="14">{\an1}<font color="#484f59">You know what to do, Kadoma</font></font></font></font>

200
00:11:33,500 --> 00:11:35,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="14">{\an1}<font color="#484f59">Don't screw it up</font></font></font></font>

201
00:11:36,770 --> 00:11:37,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay...</font>

202
00:11:38,380 --> 00:11:42,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nakao, your personality sucks,
 but you sure are cute.</font>

203
00:11:43,510 --> 00:11:45,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can't fault me for anything else,</font>

204
00:11:45,180 --> 00:11:47,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I'll give you that much!</font>

205
00:11:48,800 --> 00:11:50,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't wait for this to be over.</i></font>

206
00:11:50,720 --> 00:11:52,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ashiya-senpai.</font>

207
00:11:53,180 --> 00:11:55,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're Kadoma from Dorm 1, right?</font>

208
00:11:55,940 --> 00:11:56,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

209
00:11:56,860 --> 00:11:59,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-Actually, I'd like to talk to you.</font>

210
00:11:59,690 --> 00:12:00,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To me?</font>

211
00:12:00,970 --> 00:12:01,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes!</font>

212
00:12:01,920 --> 00:12:02,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please.</font>

213
00:12:09,130 --> 00:12:12,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you're on the karate team, right?</font>

214
00:12:12,380 --> 00:12:14,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, uh, yeah.</font>

215
00:12:14,890 --> 00:12:17,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What made you join?</font>

216
00:12:18,410 --> 00:12:20,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, you don't exactly 
look like the type.</font>

217
00:12:20,450 --> 00:12:22,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I'm so sorry!</font>

218
00:12:22,190 --> 00:12:23,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine.</font>

219
00:12:24,460 --> 00:12:29,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I get mistaken for a girl a lot in town,</font>

220
00:12:29,020 --> 00:12:32,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and I'm the only one of my siblings 
who's small and weak.</font>

221
00:12:33,120 --> 00:12:36,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But then I saw Kujo-senpai's kumite.</font>

222
00:12:37,000 --> 00:12:38,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kujo?</font>

223
00:12:38,650 --> 00:12:42,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was just so... How should I put it?
 It was beautiful.</font>

224
00:12:43,740 --> 00:12:45,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was moved.</font>

225
00:12:48,320 --> 00:12:51,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know that's probably weird.</font>

226
00:12:51,230 --> 00:12:52,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I get it.</font>

227
00:12:53,490 --> 00:12:55,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have a similar story.</font>

228
00:12:55,330 --> 00:12:56,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ashiya-senpai?</font>

229
00:12:59,110 --> 00:13:01,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Senpai, um, the truth is—</font>

230
00:13:01,420 --> 00:13:03,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good job, Kadoma.</font>

231
00:13:06,730 --> 00:13:09,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kadoma, you can go back now.</font>

232
00:13:18,730 --> 00:13:20,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, come <b>on</b>!</font>

233
00:13:20,720 --> 00:13:24,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're about to make the announcement 
at the stage... Where'd he get off to?</font>

234
00:13:24,290 --> 00:13:25,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let go of me!</font>

235
00:13:25,740 --> 00:13:27,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop resisting and come with us!</font>

236
00:13:26,590 --> 00:13:27,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I said let me go!</font>

237
00:13:27,990 --> 00:13:29,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ashiya?</font>

238
00:13:29,120 --> 00:13:30,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, you there!</font>

239
00:13:30,530 --> 00:13:31,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Unhand him!</font>

240
00:13:31,680 --> 00:13:33,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you think you're doing?</font>

241
00:13:33,620 --> 00:13:34,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nakao-kun?</font>

242
00:13:34,870 --> 00:13:37,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up! Stay out of this!</font>

243
00:13:37,970 --> 00:13:39,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ignore him! Let's go!</font>

244
00:13:39,310 --> 00:13:40,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How dare you...</font>

245
00:13:40,400 --> 00:13:42,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">do that...</font>

246
00:13:42,290 --> 00:13:43,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to my face!</font>

247
00:13:43,620 --> 00:13:44,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You bastard!</font>

248
00:13:44,870 --> 00:13:46,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do something about him!</font>

249
00:13:46,920 --> 00:13:47,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">R-Right!</font>

250
00:13:47,810 --> 00:13:50,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What, you wanna go?!</font>

251
00:13:50,890 --> 00:13:52,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's finally time to announce the results!</font>

252
00:13:52,970 --> 00:13:55,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'd like to invite our twelve finalists
back to the stage, comment!</font>

253
00:13:55,880 --> 00:13:58,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give it up for them!</font>

254
00:13:58,130 --> 00:13:58,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mizuki!</font>

255
00:14:00,400 --> 00:14:02,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mizuki! Where are you?</font>

256
00:14:02,050 --> 00:14:03,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nakatsu!</font>

257
00:14:05,330 --> 00:14:07,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nakao! What's happened?!</font>

258
00:14:07,900 --> 00:14:10,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ashiya got kidnapped by guys from Dorm 1!</font>

259
00:14:10,910 --> 00:14:13,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

260
00:14:13,280 --> 00:14:14,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where'd they go?!</font>

261
00:14:14,360 --> 00:14:15,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know!</font>

262
00:14:15,660 --> 00:14:18,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I barely got away myself.</font>

263
00:14:18,680 --> 00:14:20,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Izumi!</font>

264
00:14:20,850 --> 00:14:21,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey.</font>

265
00:14:22,520 --> 00:14:24,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where did you take Ashiya?</font>

266
00:14:25,810 --> 00:14:27,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you talking about?</font>

267
00:14:27,290 --> 00:14:28,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop playing around.</font>

268
00:14:30,790 --> 00:14:32,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Wait, what's this?</font>

269
00:14:32,520 --> 00:14:34,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where's contestant 15, Kadoma-kun, going?</font>

270
00:14:35,360 --> 00:14:36,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please wait!</font>

271
00:14:37,120 --> 00:14:39,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kujo-senpai had nothing to do with this!</font>

272
00:14:40,280 --> 00:14:43,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kadoma, tell us everything you know.</font>

273
00:14:49,430 --> 00:14:51,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you guys trying to pull?!</font>

274
00:14:51,690 --> 00:14:57,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We must win at all costs
for Dorm 1's honor.</font>

275
00:14:57,070 --> 00:14:58,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kitahanada!</font>

276
00:14:58,930 --> 00:15:00,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This isn't personal.</font>

277
00:15:00,780 --> 00:15:05,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We just can't have you running 
in the 2,000-meter race.</font>

278
00:15:05,590 --> 00:15:08,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Does Tennoji know about this?!</font>

279
00:15:10,390 --> 00:15:12,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He doesn't have the slightest clue.</font>

280
00:15:13,590 --> 00:15:15,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This was all my idea.</font>

281
00:15:15,710 --> 00:15:16,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Watch him!</font>

282
00:15:16,940 --> 00:15:17,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes!</font>

283
00:15:25,320 --> 00:15:26,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This way!</font>

284
00:15:26,470 --> 00:15:29,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't tell me it was 
Kitahanada and the others...</font>

285
00:15:29,260 --> 00:15:30,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was.</font>

286
00:15:30,830 --> 00:15:32,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's always like this.</i></font>

287
00:15:32,960 --> 00:15:36,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Whenever I think something's happening 
to him when he's out of my sight,</i></font>

288
00:15:36,350 --> 00:15:38,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I get sick with worry.</i></font>

289
00:15:39,020 --> 00:15:40,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why can't you just...</i></font>

290
00:15:40,580 --> 00:15:42,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>stay by my side?</i></font>

291
00:15:44,430 --> 00:15:46,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me out of here!</font>

292
00:15:50,410 --> 00:15:51,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Behave yourself.</font>

293
00:15:56,100 --> 00:15:57,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This brat!</font>

294
00:15:57,220 --> 00:16:00,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Naniwabushi Kick!</font>

295
00:16:00,090 --> 00:16:00,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh shit!</font>

296
00:16:00,990 --> 00:16:03,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hold it right there!</font>

297
00:16:03,910 --> 00:16:05,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who the hell are you?</font>

298
00:16:06,990 --> 00:16:08,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sano!</font>

299
00:16:26,670 --> 00:16:30,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What's gotten into you?</font>

300
00:16:31,460 --> 00:16:32,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please don't move.</font>

301
00:16:35,820 --> 00:16:37,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sano...?</font>

302
00:16:40,130 --> 00:16:45,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's me... I'm the one
who wants you at my side.</i></font>

303
00:16:50,650 --> 00:16:53,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Captain, about the 2,0000-meter race...</font>

304
00:16:53,290 --> 00:16:54,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Before that...</font>

305
00:16:55,000 --> 00:16:57,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since our top three 
contestants left the stage,</font>

306
00:16:57,450 --> 00:17:03,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">victory goes to "Contestant 34-kun" of
Dorm 3 who wished to stay anonymous!</font>

307
00:17:03,820 --> 00:17:07,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll get you back for this, Nanba Minami!</i></font>

308
00:17:07,670 --> 00:17:09,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why isn't Kadoma up there?!</font>

309
00:17:09,780 --> 00:17:11,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? That can't be...</font>

310
00:17:11,100 --> 00:17:12,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Senpai.</font>

311
00:17:14,660 --> 00:17:16,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kadoma, you...</font>

312
00:17:16,620 --> 00:17:21,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kitahanada, such stunts 
aren't going to please Tennoji.</font>

313
00:17:22,120 --> 00:17:23,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What does he mean by that?</font>

314
00:17:26,160 --> 00:17:28,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so sorry!</font>

315
00:17:28,180 --> 00:17:33,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, the captured princess was freed, 
and the mastermind was caught.</font>

316
00:17:34,050 --> 00:17:36,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All's well that ends well.</font>

317
00:17:36,190 --> 00:17:37,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As for you...</font>

318
00:17:37,620 --> 00:17:39,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What happened to being in the pageant?!</font>

319
00:17:39,820 --> 00:17:41,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wah!</font>

320
00:17:41,080 --> 00:17:42,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so sorry.</font>

321
00:17:42,310 --> 00:17:44,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This was all my fault.</font>

322
00:17:44,070 --> 00:17:46,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! Why aren't you apologizing?!</font>

323
00:17:46,930 --> 00:17:48,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We are so sorry!</font>

324
00:17:48,910 --> 00:17:51,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Their crimes fall on my head!</font>

325
00:17:51,740 --> 00:17:53,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The responsibility is entirely mine!</font>

326
00:17:53,620 --> 00:17:56,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As our dorm RA 
and captain of the karate team!</font>

327
00:17:56,980 --> 00:17:58,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ashiya, what do you want to do?</font>

328
00:17:58,720 --> 00:18:04,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, well... they've apologized, 
so I'll forgive them.</font>

329
00:18:04,720 --> 00:18:07,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then I've got nothing to add.</font>

330
00:18:09,110 --> 00:18:12,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nanba, you're unbelievable...</font>

331
00:18:13,000 --> 00:18:17,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you lot will take responsibility 
for sullying the name of the karate team.</font>

332
00:18:17,070 --> 00:18:18,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-Sir!</font>

333
00:18:18,490 --> 00:18:20,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good. Now get going.</font>

334
00:18:20,720 --> 00:18:21,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sir!</font>

335
00:18:22,480 --> 00:18:23,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry, Kujo-san.</font>

336
00:18:23,690 --> 00:18:27,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was convinced you were 
the person behind this.</font>

337
00:18:27,000 --> 00:18:29,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, whenever we made eye contact,</font>

338
00:18:29,590 --> 00:18:31,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you'd give me this grin.</font>

339
00:18:34,970 --> 00:18:37,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, he literally only thinks about karate,</font>

340
00:18:37,080 --> 00:18:38,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so if he sees someone with potential,</font>

341
00:18:38,650 --> 00:18:40,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">he always wants to go and scout them.</font>

342
00:18:40,750 --> 00:18:43,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean that's why you felt up my leg?</font>

343
00:18:43,470 --> 00:18:48,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The 2,000-meter relay race is about 
to begin on the main grounds.</i></font>

344
00:18:48,240 --> 00:18:50,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>All participants, please gather there.</i></font>

345
00:18:51,220 --> 00:18:53,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're up, Ashiya and Nakatsu.</font>

346
00:18:53,190 --> 00:18:55,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No rest for the weary.</font>

347
00:18:55,380 --> 00:18:56,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go, Nakatsu.</font>

348
00:18:56,410 --> 00:18:57,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

349
00:18:57,630 --> 00:18:58,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ow!</font>

350
00:18:58,640 --> 00:19:00,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you okay?</font>

351
00:19:00,040 --> 00:19:03,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was thinkin' my leg felt weird...</font>

352
00:19:03,940 --> 00:19:06,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess it's from doing
that flying kick earlier.</font>

353
00:19:06,330 --> 00:19:08,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like I sprained it.</font>

354
00:19:08,960 --> 00:19:10,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is bad.</font>

355
00:19:10,620 --> 00:19:11,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do we do about the relay?</font>

356
00:19:14,130 --> 00:19:15,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess we have no choice.</font>

357
00:19:15,520 --> 00:19:18,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And now, our final event:
the 2,000-meter relay!</i></font>

358
00:19:18,950 --> 00:19:21,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The team who comes in first
will receive 50 points.</i></font>

359
00:19:21,120 --> 00:19:24,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Second place will get 30 points,
 and third place will get 10.</i></font>

360
00:19:24,960 --> 00:19:28,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There's still a chance for an upset!</i></font>

361
00:19:24,960 --> 00:19:28,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="16"><font color="#8b7d91">Dorm 1\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hDorm 2\h\h\h\h\h\h\hDorm 3</font></font></font></font>

362
00:19:28,460 --> 00:19:31,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hence, I'll be covering for you.</font>

363
00:19:31,560 --> 00:19:33,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you sure you can do this?!</font>

364
00:19:33,500 --> 00:19:36,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now that I've decided to enter,
of course we're going for the win.</font>

365
00:19:36,980 --> 00:19:39,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eyes on the prize until the very end!</font>

366
00:19:39,530 --> 00:19:42,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And once this is done, 
I'll be ready to get over it.</font>

367
00:19:43,410 --> 00:19:45,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've finally decided to accept it.</font>

368
00:19:46,480 --> 00:19:50,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll even send a bouquet to her wedding.</font>

369
00:19:50,830 --> 00:19:52,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Senpai...</i></font>

370
00:19:52,490 --> 00:19:56,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>All teams, on your marks!</i></font>

371
00:19:56,130 --> 00:19:58,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ashiya, I'm counting on you as our anchor.</font>

372
00:19:58,870 --> 00:19:59,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

373
00:19:59,610 --> 00:20:00,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go.</font>

374
00:20:01,120 --> 00:20:02,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good luck!</font>

375
00:20:02,800 --> 00:20:04,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're rooting for you!</font>

376
00:20:04,370 --> 00:20:06,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good luck, Senpai!</font>

377
00:20:16,820 --> 00:20:18,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sano...</i></font>

378
00:20:18,780 --> 00:20:19,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ashiya!</font>

379
00:20:19,630 --> 00:20:20,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yeah!</font>

380
00:20:20,820 --> 00:20:22,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going!</font>

381
00:20:23,520 --> 00:20:26,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We're on the third leg, 
and Dorm 1 is in the lead!</i></font>

382
00:20:26,520 --> 00:20:29,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Dorm 2 now passes 
the baton to their fourth runner!</i></font>

383
00:20:30,540 --> 00:20:32,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And there's the hand-off!</i></font>

384
00:20:32,050 --> 00:20:35,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Their fourth runner, Nanba, 
has just rounded the third corner!</i></font>

385
00:20:35,450 --> 00:20:36,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And he's fast!</i></font>

386
00:20:36,950 --> 00:20:40,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's overtaking people 
and closing the hundred-meter gap!</i></font>

387
00:20:40,700 --> 00:20:42,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's now in second place!</i></font>

388
00:20:42,810 --> 00:20:43,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ashiya!</font>

389
00:20:49,050 --> 00:20:50,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The baton switches hands!</i></font>

390
00:20:51,400 --> 00:20:53,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm counting on you, Ashiya!</font>

391
00:20:53,050 --> 00:20:54,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's like the wind!</i></font>

392
00:20:54,570 --> 00:20:56,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's quickly closing in on the lead!</i></font>

393
00:20:58,410 --> 00:20:59,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And he's out front!</i></font>

394
00:21:02,070 --> 00:21:04,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ashiya wins!</i></font>

395
00:21:04,570 --> 00:21:07,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="16"><font color="#8b7d91">Dorm 1\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hDorm 2\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hDorm 3</font></font></font></font>

396
00:21:05,010 --> 00:21:07,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Dorm 2 turns the tables 
and takes the crown!</i></font>

397
00:21:12,060 --> 00:21:13,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Thank you for your patience!</i></font>

398
00:21:13,320 --> 00:21:15,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The votes for MVP have just been tallied.</i></font>

399
00:21:15,820 --> 00:21:23,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And this year's MVP award goes 
to Dorm 2's... second-year Class C!</i></font>

400
00:21:23,370 --> 00:21:24,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We did it!</font>

401
00:21:24,650 --> 00:21:25,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right!</font>

402
00:21:32,400 --> 00:21:35,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a long day.</font>

403
00:21:36,150 --> 00:21:37,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah...</font>

404
00:21:37,130 --> 00:21:40,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on. What's up with you today?</font>

405
00:21:40,110 --> 00:21:41,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You seem really out of it.</font>

406
00:21:43,420 --> 00:21:45,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Got something on your mind?</font>

407
00:21:52,800 --> 00:21:54,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was just looking at you.</font>

408
00:21:54,700 --> 00:21:55,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

409
00:21:57,880 --> 00:22:00,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry. The wind was so loud,
I didn't catch that.</font>

410
00:22:02,930 --> 00:22:04,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come again?</font>

411
00:22:06,760 --> 00:22:08,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not telling you.</font>

412
00:22:08,130 --> 00:22:11,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Hey, come on!</font>

